item.description: I’m a sports scientist and strength and conditioning coach based in Sydney, Australia. I post my work and ideas on maximising sports performance on this site. My work and education history can be found in my one-page résumé or full CV. My most popular articles are here: https://github.com/russross/blackfriday https://github.com/alecthomas/chroma https://github.com/muesli/smartcrop https://github.com/spf13/cobra https://github.com/spf13/viper If you want to be updated when I publish something new, you can subscribe.

item.description: Hugo is the world’s fastest framework for building websites. It is written in Go.
